sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant OpenAI

    User->>Frontend: Enter Company Name & Role
    User->>Frontend: Click "Generate Cover Letter"
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/cover-letters
    Backend->>DB: Fetch Base Resume & JD
    Backend->>OpenAI: Send Resume Data + Job Context
    Note right of OpenAI: Execute Domain<br/>Traceability<br/>Validation
    OpenAI-->>Backend: Return Cover Letter + Traceability Data
    
    Backend->>Backend: Validate Traceability References
    alt References Invented Data
        Backend-->>Frontend: Generation Failed (Untruthful)
    else All References Valid
        Backend->>DB: Create CoverLetterVersion Entity
        Backend-->>Frontend: Return CoverLetterVersion
    end
